{
  "title": "ISic001106. Diodoros honours his sister Minyra",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Giorgia Capra, Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2023-07-18, in the on-site antiquarium.</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Διόδωρος Τιττέλου Ἀππειραῖος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Διόδωρος\">Διόδωρ̣ος</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τιττέλου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Τιττέλου\">Τιττέλου</span></span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"secondName\" data-text=\"Ἀππειραῖος\">Ἀππειραῖος</span></span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"τὰν\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">τὰν</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)</span><span data-text=\"ἀδελφὰν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">ἀδελφὰν</span>  <span data-text=\"αὐτοῦτα\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">αὐτοῦτα</span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μινύραν Ἀρτέμωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μινύραν\">Μινύραν</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀρτέμωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"gamonym\" data-text=\"Ἀρτέμωνος\">Ἀρτέμωνος</span></span></span>  <span data-text=\"ἱερατεύουσαν\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">ἱερατεύουσαν</span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀφροδίται Οὐρανίαι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀφροδίται\">Ἀφροδίται</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"epithet\" data-text=\"Οὐρανίαι\">Οὐρανίαι</span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Giorgia Capra, Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2023-07-18, in the on-site antiquarium.</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Διόδωρος Τιττέλου Ἀππειραῖος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Διόδωρος\">ΔΙΟΔΩ.ΟΣ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τιττέλου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Τιττέλου\">ΤΙΤΤΕΛΟΥ</span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"secondName\" data-text=\"Ἀππειραῖος\">ΑΠΠΕΙΡΑΙΟΣ</span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"τὰν\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">ΤΑΝ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span data-text=\"ἀδελφὰν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">ΑΔΕΛΦΑΝ</span><span data-text=\"αὐτοῦτα\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">ΑΥΤΟΥΤΑ</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μινύραν Ἀρτέμωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μινύραν\">ΜΙΝΥΡΑΝ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀρτέμωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"gamonym\" data-text=\"Ἀρτέμωνος\">ΑΡΤΕΜΩΝΟΣ</span></span></span><span data-text=\"ἱερατεύουσαν\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">ΙΕΡΑΤΕΥΟΥΣΑΝ</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀφροδίται Οὐρανίαι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀφροδίται\">ΑΦΡΟΔΙΤΑΙ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"epithet\" data-text=\"Οὐρανίαι\">ΟΥΡΑΝΙΑΙ</span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001106_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic001106_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001106.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic001106-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001106_copy2_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic001106_copy2_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001106_copy2.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic001106_copy2-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001106_left_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic001106_left_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001106_left.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic001106_left-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001106_leftthreequarter_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic001106_leftthreequarter_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001106_leftthreequarter.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic001106_leftthreequarter-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001106_right_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic001106_right_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001106_right.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic001106_right-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001106_rightthreequarter_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic001106_rightthreequarter_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001106_rightthreequarter.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2023-07-18\" src=\"ISic001106_rightthreequarter-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text from autopsy</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Caietanus, Gualtherus, Castelli: Διόδωτος; Ampolo-Erdas: Διόδωρος; note that the head of the rho is entirely lost.</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"2\">2: <span>Other edd: vacat not noted</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"4\">4: <span>Other edd: vacat not noted</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\" https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1030-5679\">Giorgia Capra</a></p>  <p>Diodoros Appeiraios, son of Tittelos, dedicates (a statue of) his sister Minyra, (wife?) of Artemon, priestess, to Aphrodite Ourania.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\" https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1030-5679\">Giorgia Capra</a></p>  <p>Diodoros Appeiraios, figlio di Tittelos, dedica (una statua della) sorella Minyra, (moglie?) di Artemon, sacerdotessa, a Afrodite Ourania.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>A new text (<a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001700\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001700</a>) found in 2021 in situ records the same Diodoros Appeiraios.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 45.1313 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Gualtherus 1624 262 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388</a>  </li><li> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] 321 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931</a>  </li><li> Caietanus 1707 102 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002774\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002774</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1769 cl.3 no.3 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1784 cl.3 no.4 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083</a>  </li><li> Franz 1853 5543 and p.1249 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">287</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Hoffmann 1904 5188 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817</a>  </li><li> Schmoll 1961 76-79 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001602\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001602</a>  </li><li> Agostiniani 1977 146 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002201\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002201</a>  </li><li> Giustolisi 1985 34 fig.9 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001946\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001946</a>  </li><li> Dubois 1989 <a href=\"http://www.persee.fr/doc/efr_0000-0000_1989_cat_119_1\" target=\"_blank\">213</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187</a>  </li><li> De Vido 1991 972 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001409\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001409</a>  </li><li> Nenci 1991 tav.305 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001414\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001414</a>  </li><li> De Vido 2003 397 no.1 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002041\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002041</a>  </li><li> Ampolo and Erdas 2019 G1 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Very neatly carved wide, regular letters of a fairly square module, with minimal serifs and all letters of near equal size. Straight bar alpha; epsilon with only slightly shorter middle bar; mu with vertical first and last, middle strokes descen half-way; omicron near full size; pi has equal length verticals with slight overhang on both sides of the cross bar; rho has large rounded closed eye; sigma has horizontal top and bottom strokes; phi is circular and without over-extended vertical; omega is open and tear-drop shaped.</p> <p> Types list: <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Μ-type3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Μ type3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Μ-type3.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Μ type3.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ν-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ν type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ν-type2.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ν type2.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ο-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ο type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Π-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Π type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Π-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Π type2.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Π-type2.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Π type2.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Σ-tyoe3.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Σ tyoe3.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Σ-type3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Σ type3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Υ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Υ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Υ-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Υ type2.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Φ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Φ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Φ-type2.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Φ type2.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ω-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ω type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ω-type1.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ω type1.2</a> </p> Line 1  25-34  Line 2  26-36  Line 3  24-34  Line 4  25-34  Interlineation line 1 to 2  19-21  Interlineation line 2 to 3  14-18  Interlineation line 3 to 4  10-17  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence </div>",
